org.nashua.tt151.wrappers

Class Relay

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.SensorBase
      • edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.Relay
        • org.nashua.tt151.wrappers.Relay
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LiveWindowSendable, IDevice, IDeviceController, Sendable

    public class Relay
extends Relay
    The purpose of this class is to be a wrapper for the WPILibJ Relay class. This class will at the functionality to pass a int array in the form {module, slot}. The class also adds conveniency constructors for setting the Direction.
    Version:
    2.0
    Author:
    Brian Ashworth
